snippet.title: ichigo 100% Strawberry Diary opening PS2
snippet.description:
Basically the same as the OVA opening minus a few things and with different music...

Depressing to watch.... Is it sad that one of the reasons I kept up with my Japanese is by getting into Ichigo 100%? hrmm perhaps... Anyway not enough tsukasa =[.
